description: This file declares function prototypes for the Slap Owo Loao object, including creation, removal, object enrollment, and initialization functions. It serves as an exported API for other components to interact with the SLAP Owo Loao object.

methods.name: SlapCreateOwoLoao
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Owo Loao object with specified context handles.

methods.name: SlapOwoLoaoCreate
methods.description: Allocates and initializes a new Owo Loao object.

methods.name: SlapOwoLoaoRemove
methods.description: Removes and deallocates the specified Owo Loao object.

methods.name: SlapOwoLoaoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls objects associated with the Owo Loao instance.
